ObjectStates.Name: Custom_Dice
ObjectStates.LuaScript:
rolling = false
skip_on_load = 0


function onCollisionEnter(collision_info)
  rolling = true
  skip_on_load = skip_on_load + 1
end


function onCollisionStay(collision_info)
  if rolling and skip_on_load > 2 and check_velocity(self.getVelocity()) then
    rolling = false
    Timer.destroy("broadcast_curse")
    Timer.create({
      identifier     = "broadcast_curse",
      function_name  = "broadcast_curse",
      delay          = 1
    })

  end
end

function broadcast_curse()
  broadcastToAll("Curse: " .. curse_string(self.getValue()), {0, 0, 0})
  self.setName("Curse: " .. curse_string(self.getValue()))
end

function check_velocity(velocity)
  for k,v in pairs(velocity) do
    if v > 0 then
      return false
    end
  end
  return true
end

function curse_string(val)
  local results = { "No Effect", "Lose 1 Qi", "Haunt the nearest Village Tile", "Summon a Ghost", "Lose all Tao Tokens", "No Effect"}
  return results[val]
end
